5
00:00:10.028 --> 00:00:12.170
NOVA:  Because someone's watching?

6
00:00:12.470 --> 00:00:15.630
VEGA:  Because the watchtowers never sleep.

7
00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:20.774
NULL:  I slipped a careless credential past your wall.

8
00:00:20.774 --> 00:00:23.038
Now I move in the shadows.

9
00:00:23.338 --> 00:00:26.140
VEGA:  Shadows don't last here. Every move leaves a

10
00:00:26.140 --> 00:00:26.458
mark.

11
00:00:27.508 --> 00:00:30.413
VEGA:  Layer two assumes someone got in. Now we

12
00:00:30.413 --> 00:00:33.028
see them, stop the rot, and respond.

13
00:00:33.328 --> 00:00:37.794
Three families keep watch: Audit, System Integrity, and

14
00:00:37.794 --> 00:00:39.256
Incident Response.

15
00:00:40.306 --> 00:00:43.003
NOVA:  AU, SI, IR - what do those three

16
