47
00:02:13.588 --> 00:02:17.481
NULL:  Another tower turns? Tedious. Every chain of watchers

48
00:02:17.481 --> 00:02:19.611
has a blind link - and I will

49
00:02:19.611 --> 00:02:20.786
slip through it.

50
00:02:21.836 --> 00:02:25.422
NULL:  Six days in your shadows... and you still

51
00:02:25.422 --> 00:02:27.434
