75
00:03:40.414 --> 00:03:43.087
NOVA:  Is there a plan that makes all that

76
00:03:43.087 --> 00:03:44.156
routine? IR-8?

77
00:03:45.206 --> 00:03:49.234
ARCHIVIST:  Implement an incident handling capability for incidents that

78
00:03:49.234 --> 00:03:52.523
is consistent with the incident response plan and

79
00:03:52.523 --> 00:03:57.558
includes preparation, detection and analysis, containment, eradication, and

80
00:03:57.558 --> 00:03:58.162
recovery;

81
00:03:59.212 --> 00:04:02.172
VEGA:  The best responders practiced before the fire.

82
00:04:09.512 --> 00:04:12.165
VEGA:  The Firewatch's oath. When it burns, we are

83
00:04:12.165 --> 00:04:13.152
already running.

84
00:04:14.202 --> 00:04:17.720
VEGA:  Selecting and implementing was the wall. Watching is

85
00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:18.802
