89
00:04:32.032 --> 00:04:36.341
Your options. A. AU-2 Event Logging. B. AU-9

90
00:04:36.341 --> 00:04:42.120
Protection of Audit Information. C. SI-4 System Monitoring.

91
00:04:42.420 --> 00:04:45.322
NOVA:  Pause here and lock in your answer.

92
00:04:52.372 --> 00:04:55.120
VEGA:  The answer is B. AU-9 Protection of Audit

93
00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:59.142
Information. AU-9, Protection of Audit Information, keeps an

94
00:04:59.142 --> 00:05:02.092
