95
00:05:03.142 --> 00:05:05.182
VEGA:  And who runs toward the fire?

96
00:05:05.482 --> 00:05:09.358
Which family detects, contains, and recovers from a

97
00:05:09.358 --> 00:05:09.890
breach?

98
00:05:10.190 --> 00:05:14.362
Your options. A. IR - Incident Response. B.

99
00:05:14.362 --> 00:05:17.758
AU - Audit. C. AC - Access Control.

100
00:05:18.058 --> 00:05:20.960
NOVA:  Pause here and lock in your answer.

101
00:05:28.010 --> 00:05:30.790
VEGA:  The answer is A. IR - Incident Response.

102
00:05:30.790 --> 00:05:34.613
Incident Response is the family that detects, contains,

103
00:05:34.613 --> 00:05:36.490
